<Author>Smoolander
<Content>Excellent hotel in great location My wife and I booked this hotel with less than 1 week remaining before we stayed there, and we were extremely happy with it. It is situated just off La Rambla, and is a very modern and comfortable hotel.The two bed room that we had was a good size, bigger than most others we stayed in around Europe, and was clean and modern. Wi-fi access was provided free in the room, and it also contained a small flatscreen TV on the wall.The location is fantastic, with plenty of places to eat, shop and buy souvenirs all around the hotel. Being reasonably close to La Rambla there can be a bit of noise late at night, but nothing significant enough to keep you awake.There was nothing negative to really say about the hotel, and we'd recommend it if you can get a decent price. 
