<Content>A little attention to detail would have made it so much better Great location just off the Ramblas. It is close to loads of restaurants, tourist info and metro station. The hotel is new so it is very clean but has been let down by the small details. It seems like it was finished in a rush. They have synthetic towels, the cover was still on the fire alarm in our room (which was a bit of a worry), there was no light globe in one of the bedside lamps, there were glue marks on the front of the toilet. Noise is also a bit of a problem - there are three church's around the hotel that ring there bells every hour and the nearby shops roller doors are noisy late at night. Better qualilty windows/double glazing would have fixed this. 
